description.en:
What is the project about?
A meme token with a strong meme culture

What makes your project unique?
In the encrypted world, innovation is the most needed, as a meme token, democracy is the most needed, we meet the above two points

History of your project.
This is our first project and we can't wait to prove ourselves

What’s next for your project?
Launching CEX, this is the way we have to go, and this is only the first step, Lbank+mexc+kucoin

What can your token be used for?
At present, it is still only a meme token, as a meme culture, we will launch NFT
